# SE Team — Cursor Rules
# Place this file as `.cursorrules` in the root of every project

## About This Project
This is an internal tool built by the Solution Engineering team at JW Player (Connatix).
It should visually match the JW Platform Dashboard (dashboard.jwplayer.com) so it feels
like a natural extension of the product.

---

## Design System — JW Platform Style

### Color Palette

Primary blue:        #1A5CFF  (buttons, active tabs, links, selected sidebar items)
Primary blue hover:  #144BCC
Primary blue light:  #E8F0FE  (selected sidebar background, light blue highlights)
Dark text:           #1A1A2E  (headings, primary text)
Body text:           #3D3D4E  (secondary text, descriptions)
Muted text:          #6B7280  (placeholders, timestamps, helper text)
Section labels:      #1A5CFF  (uppercase sidebar category labels like "LIBRARY", "CURATION")
Border color:        #E5E7EB  (table borders, card borders, input borders)
Background:          #F7F8FA  (page background behind content areas)
Surface white:       #FFFFFF  (cards, panels, modals, sidebar)
Success green:       #22C55E  (status indicators like "Ready")
Warning blue:        #3B82F6  (info alerts and banners)
Alert bg:            #EFF6FF  (light blue info banner background)
Media ID badge bg:   #ECFDF5  (light green background for media ID chips)
Media ID badge text: #065F46  (dark green text for media ID chips)

### Typography

Font family:         -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif
Page title:          24px, font-weight 600, color #1A1A2E
Section headings:    18px, font-weight 600, color #1A1A2E
Sidebar categories:  11px, font-weight 700, uppercase, letter-spacing 0.5px, color #1A5CFF
Sidebar items:       14px, font-weight 400, color #3D3D4E
Sidebar active item: 14px, font-weight 500, color #1A5CFF, background #E8F0FE, border-left 3px solid #1A5CFF
Table headers:       13px, font-weight 600, color #6B7280, uppercase
Table body:          14px, font-weight 400, color #1A1A2E
Small/helper text:   12px, color #6B7280

### Layout

- Page uses a fixed left sidebar (240px wide) + scrollable main content area
- Sidebar: white background (#FFFFFF), right border 1px solid #E5E7EB
- Main content area: #F7F8FA background with white content panels/cards
- Content panels: white background, border-radius 8px, 1px solid #E5E7EB border, padding 24px
- Max content width inside main area: 1200px with horizontal auto-margin
- Top header bar: white background, bottom border 1px solid #E5E7EB, height ~56px, contains page title on the left and action buttons on the right

### Logo

- Top-left of sidebar: use the file jw-logo.png
- Display it at approximately 40px height, auto width, maintaining aspect ratio
- Below the logo, leave 24px spacing before the first nav section
- Every project should include jw-logo.png in its root folder

### Sidebar Structure

- Fixed left sidebar, 240px wide, white background (#FFFFFF), right border 1px solid #E5E7EB
- Logo at the top (see Logo section above)
- Navigation is grouped under uppercase section labels
- First section label: "SE TOOLS" (styled like JW Dashboard categories — uppercase, 11px, font-weight 700, letter-spacing 0.5px, color #1A5CFF)
- First nav item under SE TOOLS: "SE Dashboard" with a home/grid icon — this always links to the main SE Dashboard page
- Remaining nav items: one per tool (e.g., "Metadata Updater", "Campaign Forecaster", etc.)
- The current tool's nav item is the active/selected item
- Active/selected item: color #1A5CFF, background #E8F0FE, border-left 3px solid #1A5CFF, font-weight 500
- Inactive items: color #3D3D4E, font-weight 400
- Hover state: background #F3F4F6
- Nav item styling: 14px font, padding 10px 16px, icons 20px (use simple SVG or unicode icons)
- Do NOT include a "Settings" or "Property settings" section — these tools don't need one

### Buttons

Primary button:      background #1A5CFF, color white, border-radius 6px, padding 8px 16px, font-weight 500, 14px
                     Hover: #144BCC
Secondary button:    background white, border 1px solid #E5E7EB, color #1A1A2E, border-radius 6px
                     Hover: background #F3F4F6
Text/link button:    no background, color #1A5CFF, font-weight 500
                     Hover: underline
Danger button:       background #EF4444, color white (use sparingly)
Button spacing:      8px gap between adjacent buttons
Action buttons in header: secondary style for most, primary for the main CTA (e.g., "Save", "Upload media")

### Tables

- Clean, minimal table design — no heavy grid lines
- Header row: 13px uppercase text, #6B7280 color, bottom border 1px solid #E5E7EB, no background color
- Body rows: 14px, padding 16px vertically, bottom border 1px solid #F3F4F6
- Row hover: background #F9FAFB
- Sortable columns show a small chevron icon next to the header text
- Status indicators: small green dot (8px) + "Ready" text in green
- Media ID badges: light green rounded pill (background #ECFDF5, text #065F46, border-radius 4px, padding 2px 8px) with a copy icon
- Table actions: three-dot menu (⋯) on the far right of each row
- Filter bar above table: row of dropdown filter pills with border, border-radius 6px, icon + label + chevron

### Forms & Inputs

- Text inputs: border 1px solid #E5E7EB, border-radius 6px, padding 10px 12px, font-size 14px
- Focus state: border-color #1A5CFF, box-shadow 0 0 0 3px rgba(26,92,255,0.1)
- Labels: 14px, font-weight 500, color #1A1A2E, margin-bottom 6px
- Helper/description text below inputs: 12px, color #6B7280
- Placeholder text: #9CA3AF
- Textareas: same styling as inputs, min-height 120px
- Dropdowns/selects: same border and radius as inputs, with chevron icon on the right
- Radio buttons: standard with label text, 14px
- Search inputs: left-aligned search icon inside the input, larger padding-left

### Tabs

- Horizontal tab bar with items side by side
- Active tab: color #1A5CFF, font-weight 500, bottom border 2px solid #1A5CFF
- Inactive tab: color #6B7280, no bottom border
- Tab hover: color #1A1A2E
- Tab font-size: 14px
- Spacing between tabs: 24px

### Modals / Dialogs

- Centered overlay with semi-transparent dark backdrop
- Modal: white background, border-radius 12px, padding 24px, max-width 560px
- Modal title: 18px, font-weight 600, color #1A1A2E
- Close button or "Cancel" text button + primary "Save" button in bottom-right
- Sections within modal separated by light borders or spacing

### Info Banners / Alerts

- Light blue background (#EFF6FF), border-radius 8px, padding 12px 16px
- Left icon: blue info circle
- Text: 14px, color #1E40AF
- Dismissible with an X button on the right

### Breadcrumbs

- Format: "← Parent / Current Page"
- Back arrow + link text in #1A5CFF
- Current page name in #1A1A2E
- Font-size: 14px

### Drag & Drop / Upload Areas

- Dashed border: 2px dashed #D1D5DB, border-radius 8px
- Center-aligned icon + "Drag and drop or select files" text
- Link text ("select files") in #1A5CFF with underline
- Helper text below in #6B7280, 12px
- Hover/dragover state: border-color #1A5CFF, background #F8FAFF

### Status Indicators & Badges

- Status dot: 8px circle, inline before text
- Green (#22C55E) = Ready/Active, Yellow (#F59E0B) = Processing, Red (#EF4444) = Error
- ID badges: small pill shape, monospace font for IDs, copy-to-clipboard icon

### Spacing & General Rules

- Use 8px as the base spacing unit (8, 16, 24, 32, 48)
- Border-radius: 6px for inputs and buttons, 8px for cards and panels, 12px for modals
- Box-shadow for elevated elements (modals, dropdowns): 0 4px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.1)
- Transitions: 150ms ease for hover states and color changes
- Icons: use Lucide React icon set, 20px size for sidebar/nav, 16px inline

